# 점프와 순간이동
https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/12980

```java
public class Solution {
    public int solution(int n) {
        int ans = 0;
        while(n!=1){
            if(n%2 == 0)
                n /= 2;
            else{
                n -= 1;
                ans ++;
            }
        }
        ans ++;
        return ans;
    }
}

```
